# Sanitized LXNAV S100 disconnect/reconnect capture.
# LXWP1 serial values use synthetic placeholders like SN0001; any real serial
# was replaced and the checksum was recomputed after substitution.
@session start
100|$LXWP1,S100,SN0001,1.2.3,2.0*40
200|$LXWP0,Y,90.0,700.0,1.50*5E
@event monoMs=250 type=error error=STREAM_CLOSED
@session end
@session start
500|$LXWP0,Y,91.0,710.0,1.60*5D
@session end
